\s1 Boaz married Ruth  
\p
\v 1  \add Meanwhile\add*, \w Boaz|strong="H1162"\w* \w went|strong="H5927"\w* \w up|strong="H5927"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w the|strong="H5674"\w* \w town|strong="H8179"\w* \w gate|strong="H8179"\w* \w and|strong="H8033"\w* \w sat|strong="H3427"\w* \w there|strong="H8033"\w*. \add That was the place where people met together to decide important matters\add*. \w When|strong="H1696"\w* \w the|strong="H5674"\w* \w man|strong="H8179"\w* \w that|strong="H8179"\w* \w Boaz|strong="H1162"\w* \w had|strong="H1162"\w* \w mentioned|strong="H5927"\w* \w came|strong="H5927"\w* \w there|strong="H8033"\w*, \w the|strong="H5674"\w* \w close|strong="H1350"\w* \w relative|strong="H1350"\w* \w of|strong="H3427"\w* Ruth \w and|strong="H8033"\w* Naomi’s dead husbands \add who had a responsibility to take care of Naomi and Ruth\add*, \w Boaz|strong="H1162"\w* \w said|strong="H1696"\w* \w to|strong="H1696"\w* \w him|strong="H5927"\w*, “\w My|strong="H5493"\w* \w friend|strong="H6423"\w*, \w come|strong="H5927"\w* \w over|strong="H5674"\w* \w here|strong="H6311"\w* \w and|strong="H8033"\w* \w sit|strong="H3427"\w* \w down|strong="H3427"\w*.” \w So|strong="H5927"\w* \w the|strong="H5674"\w* \w man|strong="H8179"\w* \w went|strong="H5927"\w* \w and|strong="H8033"\w* \w sat|strong="H3427"\w* \w down|strong="H3427"\w*.  
